r the COVID-19-hit edition in Tokyo in 2021 and the corruption-tainted Rio de Janeiro Games in 2016, the Paris Olympics are seen as an important moment for the sporting extravaganza.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9996360994294484, \"rank\": 0.0003382078307570835, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}, {\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997962732, \"rank\": 2.0355777007512848e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6422905079315536e-24, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"an important moment\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting extravaganza\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the background in Marseille, around 6,000 security forces are on duty at a time when the country is on its highest terror alert.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999997446457527, \"rank\": 2.5535429162625023e-07, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/